Passive: If Draven has an empowered axe in hand, his next attack will throw it. On takedown, gain an Adoration stack, doubled if Draven or Darius scored the kill. Every 11 Adoration stacks grants 1/3/5 Gold.

Active: Spin an empowered axe that replaces his basic attack and deals physical damage and returns to Draven after hitting an enemy.

flatData.name: Double Trouble Bubble
flatData.description:
Passive: Damaging an enemy applies 30% Shred for 6 seconds.

Active: Zoe kicks 2 bubbles at nearby enemies, dealing magic damage and 30% Chilling them for 3 seconds.

flatData.name: Visions of the End
flatData.description:
Zilean throws a Time Bomb on the nearest enemy without one. Time Bombs deal magic damage each second. When the target dies, they explode, dealing magic damage in a 1 hex radius and grant Zilean 15 mana.

If a Time Bomb is on an enemy for 18/16/1 seconds and Zilean is alive, the enemy instantly dies.

flatData.name: Orbital Ordinance
flatData.description:
Passive: Ziggs attacks are bouncing bombs that deal magic damage to the first enemy hit.

Active: Deal (AP) magic damage in a 1- hex radius centered on the target.

flatData.name: Kin of the Stained Blade
flatData.description:
Passive: Attacks alternate between dealing bonus physical damage and bonus magic damage.

Active: Yone strikes through the most enemies possible within 3 hexes, knocking them up for 1.5 seconds and dealing physical damage and magic damage. Yone then splits physical damage and magic damage among all enemies hit.

Blade Brothers: When you field Yasuo and Yone, Yasuo assists Yone's casts. Blade Brothers: When Yone casts, your strongest Yasuo blinks to each target, dealing bonus physical damage

flatData.name: Blade of the Ruined King
flatData.description:
Passive: Viego gains ]% (Souls) Attack Speed.

Active: Deal physical damage to target. For the rest of combat, Viego's attacks deal bonus stacking magic damage.

flatData.name: Undying Rage
flatData.description:
Tryndamere becomes enraged for 5 seconds. While enraged, gain (AP) Durability and attacks are replaced with a strike that deals physical damage. Ignore 0.3% of Armor against Chilled enemies.

Bloodsword Bond: When you field Ashe and Tryndamere, your strongest copies permanently increase their power on kill.>Bloodsword Bond: Gain increased Move Speed. Gain 0.1% Attack Damage, permanently increased by 0.01% whenever Ashe or Tryndamere score a kill.

flatData.name: The Box
flatData.description:
Passive: Each second, Thresh deals (AP & Souls) magic damage to all enemies within 2 hexes. Heal for 0.4% of the damage dealt by this effect.

Active: Create a prison of walls in a 2 hex radius that lasts 5/5/60 seconds. While active, the Passive's damage is doubled. When an enemy touches a wall, they take magic damage. If there are less than 2 enemies inside The Box at any time, drag an enemy in.

flatData.name: Stolen Might
flatData.description:
Sylas casts one of three spells:

Cataclysm: Leap on a nearby enemy. Deal magic damage to all enemies within 2 hexes and Stun them for 1.5/1.75/30 seconds.

Demacian Justice: Deal magic damage to target. If they are below 0.15% max Health, execute them.

Final Spark: Gain 400/450/800 (AP) Shield for 2 seconds. Deal magic damage to all enemies in a line.

flatData.name: Nevermove
flatData.description:
Passive: Each second, Swain restores Health and deals magic damage to enemies within 1 Hex. 

Active: Open a demonic eye on the largest group of nearby enemies, dealing magic damage and Stunning them for 1.75/2/8 seconds.

flatData.name: Grand Encore
flatData.description:
Seraphine gains 3 notes. For each one active, deal magic damage to a nearby enemy.

While holding 12 notes on cast, consume them to project a wave of energy. Allies hit restore Health. Enemies hit take magic damage, reduced by 0.3% for each enemy it's passed through.

flatData.name: Runic Overload
flatData.description:
Ryze releases a runic blast, dealing magic damage. It splits in two, dealing 0.33% of the damage to the closest two enemies. Each secondary blast splits an additional time.
* Bilgewater  blasts explode on impact, dealing % as Physical Damage to adjacent enemies.
* Demacia  Execute targets below % (ArmorMR).
* Freljord  Chill targets for a few seconds and deal bonus true damage.
* Ionia  Blasts split an additional time.
* Ixtal  Gain a random Region's effect on combat start and every 10 seconds.
* Noxus  Blasts now pierce targets, dealing % reduced damage per enemy hit.
* Piltover  Every third cast is Overcharged, dealing % more damage.
* Shadow Isles  Increase blast damage by X Souls.
* Shurima  Knock up enemies with a chance to dredge up Gold or Treasures.
* Targon  Heal the lowest  ally for % of the damage dealt.
* Void  Ignore % of enemies' Armor and Magic Resistance.
* Yordle  Shrink targets hit, lowering their damage by % for a few seconds.
* Zaun  Poison targets, dealing Magic Damage over a few seconds.

flatData.name: Warp Armor
flatData.description: Rift Herald gains max Health and grow larger. Slam in a 2 Hex circle on the target, dealing magic damage to enemies hit. For 4 seconds, gain (AP) Durability + 0.01% for each enemy targeting this unit.

flatData.name: Fury of the Sands
flatData.description: Nasus steals Health split between the 4/4/8 nearest enemies. For 8 seconds, gain 30 Armor and Magic Resist and deal 0.015/0.015/0.12 (Health) magic damage to adjacent enemies each second.

flatData.name: Final Spark
flatData.description: Lux fires a ball of light at the most enemies, dealing magic damage to the first 2 enemies hit and Rooting them for 1 second. Then fire a beam, dealing magic damage to enemies hit by the ball and magic damage to all other enemies hit.

flatData.name: The Culling
flatData.description: Fire (AS) shots towards target. Each shot explodes on the first enemy hit, dealing physical damage to all nearby enemies. If an enemy is afflicted with Black Mist, purify them, immediately draining their Armor for the total amount.

flatData.name: Solar Flare
flatData.description:
Passive: Reduce instances of incoming damage.

Active: Leona calls down sun beams on the 3 nearest enemies, Stunning them for 1 second and dealing magic damage. Wound and 1% Burn them for 4 seconds..

flatData.name: Distortions
flatData.description: LeBlanc summons 3 dashing mirror images that strike the target and up to other nearby enemies. The target takes magic damage and is Stunned for 1 second, while other units hit take magic damage.

flatData.name: Lamb's Respite
flatData.description:
Kindred dashes, then create a 2-hex radius zone for 2.5/2.5/99 seconds that prevents allies within from dying. While active, double current Attack Speed and on attack, fire a secondary arrow at a nearby enemy that deals physical damage. 

When the zone ends, heal all allies for 0.08 (AP) of damage dealt while it was up and dash away.

flatData.name: Slicing Maelstrom
flatData.description: Kennen gains a Shield and summon storm of lightning. 6 waves of bolts hit enemies within, dealing magic damage over 3 seconds. The first 3 targets to be struck by 3 bolts are Stunned for 1.5 seconds. Multiple Stuns on the same enemy have 0.5% effectiveness.

flatData.name: Icathian Rain
flatData.description: Kai'Sa dashes away from all enemies, then fire 15/15/25 missiles split across the 4 nearest enemies. Each missile deals physical damage.

flatData.name: Curtain Call
flatData.description: For the next 4 attacks, Jhin gains infinite range and replace attacks with a cannon shot. Cannon shots deal physical damage. The 4th shot deals 1.44% more damage.

flatData.name: Snip Snip!
flatData.description: Gwen dashes around target and snip (X Souls) times, dealing magic damage to them and damage to all other enemies in a cone.

flatData.name: Judgment
flatData.description: Garen spins for 3 seconds, gaining 55% Durability and healing for over the duration. Each second, deal physical damage to adjacent enemies and reduce their Armor and Magic Resistance by 5.

flatData.name: Powder Kegs
flatData.description: Gangplank tosses barrels at the 3 nearest enemies and detonate them. They deal damage, reduced by 0.2% for each barrel in the chain. Barrels reduce their target's Armor by 10, increased to 30 if the damage critically strikes.

flatData.name: Inspirational Might
flatData.description:
Passive: Every 3rd attack deals 4/6/90 (MR) magic damage in a circle around the target.

Active: Galio dashes into the largest group of units and inspire all allies within 2 hexes, granting them a Shield for 4 seconds. Then crash down, dealing 5/7.5/50 (MR) bonus magic damage to all enemies with 2 hexes.

flatData.name: Playful Trickster
flatData.description: Fizz becomes briefly untargetable, then jump to the farthest enemy within 4 hexes and deal  magic damage to adjacent enemies. For the next 4 attacks, gain 0.5% Attack Speed and deal bonus magic damage on hit.

flatData.name: Crowstorm
flatData.description: Fiddlesticks teleports into the largest cluster of enemies and Stun them. Begin losing 20 mana per second. While casting, deal magic damage per second to all enemies within a 2 hex radius. The closest 2 enemies take 0.33% more damage.

flatData.name: Parallel Convergence
flatData.description:
Ekko creates a 1 hex zone around the target that lasts 3 seconds. The next 3 attacks deal bonus magic damage. 

When the zone ends, it deals magic damage + 0.1% of the target's damage taken during the duration to all enemies in the zone.

flatData.name: Decimate
flatData.description:
Darius restores Health and spin, dealing physical damage to adjacent enemies and applying a stack of Hemorrhage that deals 15/25/40 (AD) physical damage each second for 4 seconds.

If an enemy with Hemorrhage drops below 0.08% Health, slam on them, instantly killing them. (Each stack increases the execute threshold by 0.05%)

flatData.name: Rupture
flatData.description: Cho'Gath restores Health and rupture a 2 hex circle beneath target. After a brief delay, enemies within are knocked up for 1.5 seconds and take 0.05 + 45/75/110 (Health & AP) magic damage.

flatData.name: Static Field
flatData.description: Blitzcrank gains a Shield for 4 seconds and deal 1.4/2.1/3.15 (MR) magic damage to all enemies within 1 hex.

flatData.name: Endless Banquet
flatData.description:
Passive: On takedown, Bel'Veth gains 0.7/0.7/2% stacking Attack Speed that decays over 3 seconds.

Active: Deal physical damage in a 2 hex radius and transform for the rest of combat.

While transformed, gain 0.33/0.33/1.33 (AP) Attack Speed, 0.33% max Health, and increased Move Speed. Attacks deal bonus true damage, increased by 3/5/25 for each time the same enemy is hit.

flatData.name: Wrath of the Void
flatData.description:
Passive: Baron Nashor is immune to Crowd Control effects. Attacks deal damage in a line on target. If no enemies are in range, dash to the next one and knock up adjacent enemies on arrival.

While in the Void Rift, erupt a tentacle below a random enemy every 3/3/0.25 seconds that knocks them up for 1.5 seconds.

Active: Slam and erect spikes in a 2 hex circle, dealing physical damage to enemies hit. Then over 3 seconds, spit 10 globs of acid that deal physical damage.

flatData.name: Traveler's Call
flatData.description: Launch 6 Meeps at nearby enemies that deal magic damage. Add an additional Meep for each 3-star unit on your board.

flatData.name: Arise!
flatData.description:
Passive: After witnessing 3 attacks from Azir, Sand Soldiers deal magic damage to their target.

Active: Summon a Sand Soldier near target and command them to strike. If 2 Soldiers are already out, they all immediately deal magic damage instead.

flatData.name: True Ice Arrow
flatData.description:
Ashe fires an arrow at target that deals physical damage to them and to adjacent enemies. Targets below 0.3% max Health take true damage instead. 30% Chill all enemies hit for 3 seconds.

Bloodsword Bond: When you field Ashe and Tryndamere, your strongest copies permanently increase their power on kill. Bloodsword Bond: Attacks fire a bonus arrow for every 0.05% Attack Damage granted to Tryndamere by Bloodsword Bond. These arrows deal 0.07 (%i:TFTBaseAD%) physical damage.

flatData.name: Incendiary Onslaught
flatData.description:
Aphelios starts with Infernum equipped. On cast, switch to Severum for 8 (AP) attacks.

Infernum: Attacks hit 3 enemies and apply 0.3% Sunder for 6 seconds.
Severum: Gain 2% Attack Speed and 0.1% Omnivamp. Attacks are replaced with swipes that deal physical damage.

flatData.name: Enraged Inferno
flatData.description:
Erupt the entire battlefield in flames, permanently Burning and Wounding all enemies and dealing magic damage to each of them over 45 seconds. 

Annie's max Mana is reduced by 140 for the rest of combat. Subsquent casts launch a fireball at target that deals magic damage.

flatData.name: Lacerate
flatData.description: Ambessa swipes and dashes around target, dealing physical damage to enemies in the path. Then slam chains on target, dealing physical damage in a line. If any enemies are killed, immediately recast this ability, dealing 1% damage.

flatData.name: The Darkin Blade
flatData.description:
On cast, Aatrox cycles through one of the following abilities:

Slash in a line, dealing  physical damage to enemies hit and 20% Sundering them for 4 seconds.

Swipe in a cone, dealing physical damage to enemies hit and knocking them up for 1 second.

Slam on target, dealing physical damage in a 1 hex circle. Targets below 0.15% max Health are executed.

flatData.name: Poison Trail
flatData.description:
Passive: Singed runs around the battlefield, leaving a poison trail that lingers for 4 seconds. Poison trails deal  magic damage per second to enemies within. Gain 10 (AS) Mana each second.

Active: For 4 seconds, gain increased Move Speed, restore Health each second, and gain 50 Armor and Magic Resistance.

flatData.name: Divine Challenge
flatData.description:
Zaahen dashes around target and slash in a circle, dealing physical damage to target and physical damage to all other adjacent enemies hit. If the target doesn't die, immediately cast again.

If this Ability is cast 25 times in a row, instead slam on target, instantly killing them and dealing physical damage to all enemies within 3 hexes.

flatData.name: Seismic Slam
flatData.description:
Passive: Brock is immune to crowd control effects. Attacks briefly knock up the target and deal 0.5% damage in a 1 hex radius around them.

Active: Slam the ground, dealing physical damage to ALL enemies, reduced by 0.15% for each hex from the center (down to 0.4%.) If this is the first time they've been hit by Seismic Slam this combat, knock them up for up to 1.75 seconds. 12 rocks fall around the battlefield, each dealing physical damage to enemies hit.

flatData.name: The Skies Descend
flatData.description:
Passive: After dealing ability damage to an enemy, Aurelion Sol gain Stardust. Stadust makes The Skies Descend more powerful.

Active: Crash a star on target, dealing magic damage in a 2 hex radius.

flatData.name: Eye of the Ascendant
flatData.description: Xerath launches arcane blasts randomly split between the closest 4/4/10 enemies that each deal magic damage.

flatData.name: The Relentless Storm
flatData.description:
Volibear bites the target and mark them, dealing physical damage, increased by 0.6% if they are already marked. After casting 5/5/2 times, leap to a nearby hex, activating Stormbringer and dealing physical damage to enemies within a two hex radius.

Stormbringer: Gain  Health and Attack Speed. Every 2/2/0.3 seconds, summon a lightning bolt on a nearby enemy, dealing magic damage. Takedowns summon a bolt on fallen enemies.

flatData.name: Devour
flatData.description:
Tahm Kench devours a target for 2.5 seconds, dealing magic damage and making them immune to other sources of damage. During this time, gain 0.3% Durability. If they are immune to crowd control, deal 600/900/20000 (AP) magic damage instead.

If they die while devoured, spit out a random component they were holding or the unit's cost in gold. Otherwise, spit them towards the farthest enemy, briefly Stunning targets on impact.

flatData.name: Hextech Arsenal
flatData.description:
Passive: Attacks fire a barrage of 4 bullets.

Active: T-Hex gains Shield and begin consuming 33 mana per second. Each second while casting, fire a laser that deals physical damage, reduced by 0.15% per enemy hit up to 0.45%. Additionally, launch (AS) missiles split between 4 nearby enemies that each deal physical damage.

flatData.name: Dragon's Descent / Flame Breath
flatData.description:
Dragon's Descent: Shyvana transforms into a dragon, gaining max Health. Briefly gain 0.2/0.2/0.9% Durability and dive-bomb into the largest group of enemies, dealing physical damage in a 3 hex circle.

Flame Breath: Breath fire in a cone for 3.5 seconds, dealing 150/225/12345 + 20/30/1234 (AD & AP) physical damage each second to enemies hit.

flatData.name: The Show Stopper
flatData.description: Sett grabs a target and slam them forward, dealing of their max Health as magic damage to them. All other enemies within 3 hexes take 0.5% of the total damage.

flatData.name: Call of the Forge
flatData.description:
Ornn summons an elemental from behind the farthest enemy. It 20% Chills enemies hit for 3 seconds and deals magic damage to them.

When it arrives, headbutt it and redirect it toward another distant enemy, dealing magic damage instead.

flatData.name: Radiant Eclipse
flatData.description:
Passive: While gaining Mana, Mel throws out 2/2/9 radiant orbs that orbit around target. They deal magic damage in a 1 hex radius and drain 1 Mana from units hit each second. After draining 250/250/10 mana, gain a random Radiant Item.

Active: Detonate orbs on target, causing a 3 hex radius explosion that deals magic damage to them and damage to all other enemies hit.

flatData.name: Eternal Hunger
flatData.description: Warwick gains Attack Speed, 0.15% Omnivamp, increased Move Speed, and deal bonus physical damage on attack for the rest of combat. While this effect is active, takedowns grant Warwick, Jinx, and Vi 0.2/0.2/0.5 (AP) Attack Speed for 3 seconds.

flatData.name: Dark Storm
flatData.description:
Passive: Gain 0.5% more Ability Power from all sources. 

Active: Veigar calls down a storm of meteors across the battlefield that deal magic damage each. They can innately critically strike. For each one that kills an enemy, permanently gain 1 Ability Power.

flatData.name: Starlight's Touch
flatData.description:
Passive: All allies gain Magic Resist. Once per combat after dropping below 0.35% max Health, Taric gains 0.9% Durability for 2 seconds.

Active: Gain a Shield and grant the 2 lowest Health allies Shield for 4 seconds. The next 2/2/10 attacks deal bonus magic damage.

flatData.name: Impale
flatData.description:
Passive: All allies gain Armor.

Active: Skarner gains a Shield for 4 seconds. Impale up to three nearby enemies in a line, dealing 1.2/1.8/25 (Armor) physical damage and Stunning them for 2/2.25/8 seconds.

flatData.name: Slice and Dice
flatData.description: Renekton dashes to the farthest enemy within 2 hexes, dealing physical damage to all enemies in the path. Then slash 4 times, each dealing physical damage. Subsquent casts increase the number of slashes by 1.

flatData.name: Relentless Pounce
flatData.description:
Nidalee jumps on an adjacent enemy with the lowest health, then deals magic damage to them and magic damage to adjacent enemies. If any die, cast again, dealing 0.7% damage.

Tanks take 0.5% more damage from this ability and Fighters take 0.25% more.

flatData.name: Heartbreaker
flatData.description:
Passive: Miss Fortune attacks ricochet to the highest current Health enemy, dealing 0.5% damage.

Active: Fire waves of bullets that land on the 2 nearest enemies. The first wave deals  physical damage and the rest deal physical damage. Every 3rd cast, increase the number of waves by 1.

flatData.name: Frozen Tomb
flatData.description:
Lissandra encases a target in ice, Stunning them for 1.5 seconds and dealing magic damage. All enemies within 2 hexes of them split magic damage. If the target dies, shards fly out and split excess damage between the 2 nearest enemies.

Chilled enemies take 0.12% more damage from this ability.

flatData.name: Endless Rend
flatData.description: Kalista summons (Souls) spears split among the 3 nearest enemies. After a brief delay, they each impale their target, dealing physical damage and reducing Armor by 1.

flatData.name: Lunar Rush
flatData.description:
Passive: Ability damage from your strongest Leona and strongest Diana marks enemies as Moonlit, reducing their damage by 0.1%.

Active: Gain a Shield for 2 seconds. Unleash a bolt of lunar energy at the farthest non-Moonlit enemy within 4 hexes, dealing magic damage. Then, dash to all Moonlit enemies, dealing magic damage to them.

flatData.name: Unbreakable Frost
flatData.description: Braum raises a shield for 4 seconds, gaining (AP) Durability and redirecting projectiles to towards Braum instead. When hit, deal magic damage to nearby enemies and 30% Chill them for 2 seconds.

flatData.name: Tumble
flatData.description: Vayne tumbles to a nearby hex, then fire a bolt at target that deals true damage.

flatData.name: Winter's Wrath
flatData.description: Sejuani gain a Shield for 4 seconds. Strike in a cone and a line. Enemies hit take magic damage and are 30% Chilled for 4 seconds. If they are already Chilled, Stun them for 1 second.

flatData.name: Titan's Wrath
flatData.description:
Passive: Every 4 seconds and on cast, the next attack deals damage in a 1 hex circle and deals 0.9/1.35/2.15 (MR) bonus magic damage.

Active: Nautilus gains Shield for 4 seconds.

flatData.name: Ultra Mega Fire Kick!!!
flatData.description: Millio launches a fuemigo at target that bounces 3 times, dealing magic damage to enemies hit. The last bounce deals magic damage to enemies in a 1 hex radius.

flatData.name: Void Swarm
flatData.description: Malzahar summons 2 Voidlings that each attack a nearby enemy 15 times. Each attack deals magic damage.

flatData.name: Piltover Tussle
flatData.description: Loris gains a Shield for 4 seconds. Charge and knock the target backwards, Stunning them and units hit for 1.25 seconds and dealing magic damage to them. After charging, force nearby enemies to target this unit.

flatData.name: You & Me!
flatData.description:
Passive: Yuumi joins your strongest Kobuko. Every 3 seconds, she alternates between healing the lowest Health ally for Health or granting Attack Speed to the ally who has dealt the most damage for 4 seconds.

Active: Dance, restoring 100/140/200 + 0.08 (Health & AP) Health over 3 seconds.

flatData.name: Switcheroo!
flatData.description: Passive: After attacking 18/18/16 times, Jinx switches to Fishbones. While equipped, attacks are replaced with 3 rockets that target random enemies and deal physical damage.

flatData.name: Maximum Dosage
flatData.description: Dr. Mundo bulks up for 5 seconds. While bulked, restore Health every second and attacks deal physical damage.

flatData.name: Fox-Fire
flatData.description:
Ahri fires 3 flames at target, each dealing magic damage. Every 3rd cast, fire 9 flames split between the target and up to 2 nearby enemies.

If there are nearby enemies, dash away.

flatData.name: Mourning Mist
flatData.description: Yorick restores  (AP & Souls) Health. Throw a globule of black mist at the enemy who has dealt the most damage this combat, preferring unique enemies. It 20% Chills them for 4 seconds and raises the Mana cost of their next cast by 20. It then deals magic damage in 1 hex radius.

flatData.name: Sweeping Blade
flatData.description:
Yasuo dashes, then deals physical damage to adjacent enemies. If only one enemy is hit, deal double damage.

Blade Brothers: When you field Yasuo and Yone, Yasuo assists Yone's casts. Blade Brothers: When Yone casts, your strongest Yasuo blinks to every target Yone hits and deals 1% %i:TFTBaseAD% physical damage to each.

flatData.name: Three Talon Strike
flatData.description: Xin Zhao strikes his target 3 times. Each strike deals physical damage and restores Health. The final one Stuns for 1.5 seconds.

flatData.name: Stacked Deck
flatData.description:
Passive: Attacks deal bonus magic damage. After every 3rd attack, Twisted Fate throws 3 cards in a cone that deal magic damage, reduced by 0.5% for each enemy they pass through.

Partners in Crime: When you field Graves and Twisted Fate, both gain bonuses.Partners in Crime: Twisted Fate's ability marks targets for Graves. When Graves kills a marked target, gain 10% Ability Power until end of combat.

flatData.name: Buster Shot
flatData.description: Tristana fires a massive cannonball at the closest enemy, dealing physical damage. If they are within 2 hexes, knock them back 2 hexes and briefly Stun them.

flatData.name: Toxic Dart
flatData.description: Teemo shoots the closest unpoisoned enemy, dealing magic damage and poisoning them for 8 seconds. Poisoned enemies take magic damage each second.

flatData.name: Soul Furnace
flatData.description:
Passive: Takedowns grant Sion permanent max Health.

Active: Gain 0.1 (Health & AP) Shield for 4 seconds. When it breaks, deal 0.07 (Health) magic damage to adjacent enemies.

flatData.name: Burrow
flatData.description: Rek'Sai dashes to the furthest enemy within 3 hexes and deals physical damage to them. The next 3 attacks hit adjacent enemies and deal physical damage.

flatData.name: Hammer Shock
flatData.description: Poppy gains a Shield for 4 seconds and deals physical damage to target. After a delay, briefly knock them up and deal the damage again. Bucklers fly out from the target, granting 2 nearby allies 0.3% of the Shield gained.

flatData.name: Command: Protect
flatData.description:
Orianna sends the Ball to target, dealing magic damage and splitting magic damage among enemies within a 1 hex circle.

Then grant a Shield to the two lowest Health allies for 3 seconds.

flatData.name: Pop Blossom
flatData.description: Neeko leaps at target and gains Shield for 4 seconds. Slam down after a brief delay, dealing magic damage to enemies within two hexes and 20% Chilling them for 3 seconds.

flatData.name: Power Chord
flatData.description: Sona deals magic damage to 2 nearby enemies and restore Health to the lowest Health ally.

flatData.name: Stand United
flatData.description: Shen grants a Shield to this unit and a nearby damaged ally for 4 seconds.

flatData.name: Junkyard Titan
flatData.description: Rumble gains a Shield for 4 seconds. Fire a burst of flames, dealing 1.8/2.7/4.05 + 0 (Armor) magic damage in a cone.

flatData.name: Clear The Brush
flatData.description: Qiyana dashes to a nearby hex and swing forward, dealing physical damage to enemies in a 2-hex line.

flatData.name: Whimsy
flatData.description: Lulu deals magic damage to target and make them dance for 2 seconds. The projectile then bounces to the nearest target, dealing magic damage.

flatData.name: Caustic Spittle
flatData.description: Kog'Maw deals magic damage to target and reduce their Armor and Magic Resist by 8/10/15. Adjacent enemies are dealt 0.5% of the damage and effect.

flatData.name: Demacian Standard
flatData.description: Jarvan gains a Shield for 4 seconds. Grant all allies Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

flatData.name: Tentacle Smash
flatData.description: Illaoi restores Health and slam a tentacle, dealing  physical damage to enemies in a line.

flatData.name: Ace in the Hole
flatData.description: Caitlyn fires a bullet towards the farthest enemy, dealing physical damage to the first enemy it hits. If they die, the bullet ricochets, dealing excess damage to the next enemy hit.

flatData.name: Blood Frenzy
flatData.description: Briar leaps to the furthest enemy within 3 hexes. For 4 seconds gain increased Move Speed, 0.3% Attack Damage, and 3 (AP) decaying Attack Speed.

flatData.name: Frostbite
flatData.description: Anivia fires an ice shard at target that deals magic damage. If they are Chilled, the damage Critically Strikes.
